{
  "stem": "13911.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But to take-- to take the effort to really mock you, after all these boxes-- and this is on the stage, where everybody called out, now for this girl, an onion.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this explains.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, we were always in danger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anti-Semitism-- that's why we lived very much apart, because otherwise, there would have been conflict every day, all day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened is then they started-- you would hear the radio.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or you felt it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, even if you didn't have a radio, you-- you felt-- Jew, Jew, Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jew, go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a motto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Jew go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was something that you heard since.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They started talking, the Poles, about-- not the Poles like the neighbors, but the authorities-- about-- it was Hitler's influence-- to take all the Jews and send them to Madagascar.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, we knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We-- we learned geography.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Here it's not compulsory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But for us, everything was compulsory-- history, geography, everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But Madagascar was such a-- an exotic-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's such a strange, fun place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We didn't travel very far, you know, to-- to the-- like, nowadays, the world is small.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know the whole world.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But then-- so-- but we knew that it's Africa.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it's-- it's wild.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's savage.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So they wanted to take-- this was the plan circulated, that they would-- will gather up all the Jews and send them on the-- on the-- on Madagascar-- to Madagascar.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were even songs that describe-- that says-- I don't want to sing it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Madagascar, the wild country, the savage country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But maybe there it will be better, because where there is culture, there-- it's no good.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where there is culture, there is-- there is-- there were-- there is culture.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is persecution.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
